- `pnpm tsgo:core && pnpm tsgo:core:test` → no errors.
- `node scripts/run-oxlint.mjs --tsconfig config/tsconfig/oxlint.core.json src/infra/device-pairing.ts src/gateway/server-methods/nodes.ts src/gateway/server-methods/devices.ts src/gateway/server-methods/device-management-authz.ts src/gateway/server-methods/nodes.test.ts src/gateway/server/ws-connection/message-handler.ts src/gateway/server/ws-connection/message-handler.post-connect-health.test.ts` → clean.
- `git diff --check` → clean.
- Fresh `$autoreview` closeout → no accepted/actionable findings reported.

